wsapp center"><header class="opener size12 center"><!-- custom opener code lives here  --><div class="opener__container opener--center"><div class="hed-byline-date__container"><h1 class="opener__hed">Documents Show Internal Clash Before U.S. Officials Pushed to Weaken Toddler Formula Rules</h1><div class="article-meta-1 article-meta-1--center"><span class="article-meta-1__byline">by <a href="https://www.propublica.org/people/lucas-waldron">Lucas Waldron</a> and <a href="https://www.propublica.org/people/heather-vogell">Heather Vogell</a> </span><span class="article-meta-1__pubdate"><time datetime="2024-03-21">March 21, 2024</time></span></div></div><!-- comment elements below here --><div class="opener-comments__container"><div class="opener-comment" id="opener-comment__1"><span class="opener-comment__text opener-econ">Strong preference.</span></div><div class="opener-comment" id="opener-comment__2"><span class="opener-comment__text opener-health">This makes no sense.</span></div><div class="opener-comment" id="opener-comment__3"><span class="opener-comment__text opener-econ">We cannot support positive language</span></div><div class="opener-comment" id="opener-comment__4"><span class="opener-comment__text opener-health">MUST RETAIN</span></div><div class="opener-comment" id="opener-comment__5"><span class="opener-comment__text opener-health">Same comment as above.</span></div><div class="opener-comment" id="opener-comment__6"><span class="opener-comment__text opener-econ">Must have!</span></div><div class="opener-comment" id="opener-comment__7"><span class="opener-comment__text opener-health">NO. This change makes no sense.</span></div><div class="opener-comment" id="opener-comment__8"><span class="opener-comment__text opener-econ">DELETE</span></div><div class="opener-comment" id="opener-comment__9"><span class="opener-comment__text opener-health">MUST NOT DELETE.</span></div><div class="opener-comment" id="opener-comment__10"><span class="opener-comment__text ope